Headliner:

► Benzi

Your DJ's favorite DJ Benzi is at the top of his game! With a brand new edition of both his long running Future Bass series: Girl Trapz, and his brand new remix mixtape behemoth Dad Trapz, what more could you ask for? Benzi has made frequent appearances on Diplo & Friends, Sirus XM radio, DJed all over the world with his duo TWRK, and now finds himself as tastemaker and A&R at Dim Mak records.
